# See https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/ for more about ignoring files.

# Dependencies
**/node_modules/
**/venv/
**/.venv/
**/env/
**/dist/
**/build/

# Python
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/*$py.class
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.coverage
**/htmlcov/
**/.mypy_cache/

# Databases
**/db.sqlite3
**/*.db
**/*.sqlite

# Environments
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

# IDEs
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/*.swp
**/*.swo

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Logs
**/logs/
**/*.log
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
